{"tid":1602072,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"發完夢翻屋企又畀老母打同恐嚇","createTime":"2019-09-29T09:43:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T03:34:25.000Z","uid":253992,"like":75,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"affef48d85d55279d00ae16c61a46ac1eec59c24","tid":1602072,"uid":253992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T09:43:56.000Z","msg":"時隔一個月又係我呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n首先對唔住啱先四點就走咗<br />\n<br />\n翻到屋企藍絲老母係咁發癲<br />\n話我癡線被洗腦 暴徒 <br />\n之後新聞話肥手足冇意識<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟著佢就話依家咁亂寧願死人嚟換和平<br />\n我聽完極心寒 話係咪我死咗妳都冇問題？<br />\n佢話係呀 死暴徒 我生咗你呢個癡線仔出嚟<br />\n鬼唔望十一你喺解放軍面前畀坦克輾過 <br />\n你畀人拉咗 打死都唔關我事呀 <br />\n之後佢打咗我三巴同威脅攞武器打我<br />\n<br />\n利申中四咋 我知小不忍則亂大謀 <br />\n但係點面對個冇良知嘅阿媽？<br />\n依家喺出面 身無分文咁濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好徬徨"},{"pid":"82c5792c5a126fa825a1d0c9c192f7c6c6ddee1f","tid":1602072,"uid":253992,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T09:45:26.000Z","msg":"大家善用不推文呀 唔好畀我呢啲po洗走有用po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"505f99f4b1ff31e515345c6eff618eb082470cf8","tid":1602072,"uid":118647,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T09:46:04.000Z","msg":"你邊區呀？"},{"pid":"2b5bc2acc367d84665a794de2fc31e1f98067ef3","tid":1602072,"uid":253992,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"505f99f4b1ff31e515345c6eff618eb082470cf8","tid":1602072,"uid":118647,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T09:46:04.000Z","msg":"你邊區呀？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T09:46:15.000Z","msg":"大圍"},{"pid":"8af8ccbc899edcb814facbabde29c1091e8f17e8","tid":1602072,"uid":182240,"like":3,"dislike":25,"score":-22,"quote":{"pid":"82c5792c5a126fa825a1d0c9c192f7c6c6ddee1f","tid":1602072,"uid":253992,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T09:45:26.000Z","msg":"大家善用不推文呀 唔好畀我呢啲po洗走有用po<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm